OL,3,CSouthern Water gets rating downgrade
OL,4,Camid 'challenging funding conditions'
OL,6,FFitch said the negative outlook is
OL,7,Fpartly because of the risk that Ofwat
OL,8,Fwill not allow Southern Water to raise
OL,9,Fbills by as much as it wants over the
OL,10,Fnext five years, therefore worsening
OL,11,Fits financial position.
OL,13,FSouthern has asked to be allowed to
OL,14,Fraise the average consumer water bill
OL,15,Fby 84% over the coming five years
OL,16,Fversus the current level.
OL,18,FBut Ofwat indicated over the summer
OL,19,Fthat it will only allow a rise of
OL,20,Fabout 44%.
