OL,3,CSouthern Water gets rating downgrade
OL,4,Camid 'challenging funding conditions'
OL,6,FThe watchdog is set to make a final
OL,7,Fverdict on bill increases across the
OL,8,Fsector in December.
OL,10,FSouthern Water has amassed more than
OL,11,F#6 billion of debt ` making it one of
OL,12,Fthe most heavily indebted water firms
OL,13,Fin the UK behind Thames Water.
OL,15,FSouthern Water, which supplies 4.7
OL,16,Fmillion people across the south and
OL,17,Fsouth-east of England, is controlled
OL,18,Fby Macquarie, the Australian
OL,19,Finvestment bank.
