OL,3,CSouthern Water gets rating downgrade
OL,4,Camid 'challenging funding conditions'
OL,6,FMacquarie was a major investor in
OL,7,FThames Water during the years when it
OL,8,Falso piled up billions of pounds worth
OL,9,Fof debt, which has led it to seek
OL,10,Femergency funding in recent weeks to
OL,11,Fkeep the company running.
OL,13,FFitch added that a favourable decision
OL,14,Ffrom Ofwat in December could alleviate
OL,15,Fsome of the financial stress and lead
OL,16,Fto it removing the negative outlook.
OL,18,FIt comes after ratings agency Moody's
OL,19,Fseparately downgraded Southern Water's
OL,20,Fcredit rating to junk last week,
OL,21,Fputting it below investment grade.
