OL,3,CSouthern Water gets rating downgrade
OL,4,Camid 'challenging funding conditions'
OL,6,FStuart Ledger, chief financial officer
OL,7,Fof Southern Water, said: "The action
OL,8,Fby Fitch Ratings today, following a
OL,9,Fsimilar move by Moody's Ratings
OL,10,Fearlier this month, reflects the
OL,11,Fongoing challenges and uncertainty
OL,12,Ffaced by all companies operating in
OL,13,Fthe UK water and wastewater sector.
OL,15,F"Ofwat's Final Determination on 19
OL,16,FDecember should help to alleviate much
OL,17,Fof the uncertainty around the sector
OL,18,Fand enable us to continue to improve
OL,19,Four services for customers, with the
OL,20,Fsupport of our shareholders and
OL,21,Flenders."
