OL,6,FAn Ofwat spokesperson said: "We note
OL,7,FSouthern Water's engagement with
OL,8,Fcreditors in respect of its financing
OL,9,Fdocuments.
OL,11,F"We will continue to engage with the
OL,12,Fcompany and closely monitor its
OL,13,Fprogress as it delivers its turnaround
OL,14,Fplan to improve performance and
OL,15,Ffinancial resilience."
